keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein's Google account was created on December 29, 2011, with the email JeffreyEpsteinOrg@gmail.com.
The account was associated with a wide range of Google services including Gmail, Google Drive, Google Maps, Google Payments, and Google+.
The last recorded logins to the account were in April 2016.
The account recovery email was listed as 'Has Madison Account', which may refer to a separate financial or email account.
The document is labeled as 'Google Confidential and Proprietary' and appears to be a subscriber information record produced as evidence.
